item.description:
@wcmasterjaap wrote:

try it like this

@echo off COLOR 08 title trainscape "C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.5.0_07\bin\javac.exe" -cp . *.java "C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.5.0_07\bin/java.exe" server pause

or this

@echo off COLOR 08 title trainscape "C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.5.0_06\bin\javac.exe" -cp . *.java "C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.5.0_06\bin/java.exe" server pause

or this

@echo off COLOR 08 title trainscape "C:\Program Files\Java\jre1.5.0_07\bin\javac.exe" -cp . *.java "C:\Program Files\Java\jre1.5.0_07\bin/java.exe" server pause

or this

@echo off COLOR 08 title trainscape "C:\Program Files\Java\jre1.5.0_06\bin\javac.exe" -cp . *.java "C:\Program Files\Java\jre1.5.0_06\bin/java.exe" server pause
